These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-1::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, cabbage, carrot, garlic
There are 4 different favourite colors: pink, azure, grey, yellow
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, train, taxi, quad-bike
4 different games are played: go, bridge, billiard, whist
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, egyptian, canadian, indonesian
 1. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1
 2. the person who likes azure is on the right of the dutch##1
 3. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
 4. the egyptian is on the right of the dutch##1
 5. the person playing go is the person eating asparagus##1
 6. the person playing bridge is on the left of the dutch##1
 7. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
 8. the person eating carrot is on the left of the person who likes pink##1
 9. the person driving the taxi is the person eating asparagus##1
10. the canadian is the person driving the train##1
11. the person who likes pink is on the right of the indonesian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Food          | cabbage    | carrot      | asparagus  | garlic     |
| Color         | yellow    | grey   | pink | azure      |
| Transport   | train       | motorbike | taxi     | quad-bike    |
| Game   | whist | bridge         | go  | billiard    |
| Nationality           | canadian      | indonesian       | dutch | egyptian |

