.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, fanta, hot-chocolate
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, november, march, september
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, daisy, zinnia, sunflower
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, bolivar, ritmeester, vegafina
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, chess, singing, card-games
 1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 2. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far right##1
 5. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 6. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
 7. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 8. the bolivar-smoker is the person who growssunflower##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in march is the person who growszinnia##1
10. the person who growstulip is on the far right##1
11. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |       4       |
| Beverage      | coffee      | 7up     | fanta    | hot-chocolate |
| Birthday   | january | november   | march   | september           |
| Flower   | daisy  | sunflower     | zinnia    | tulip         |
| Cigar           | vegafina         | bolivar | ritmeester     | aristoff        |
| Hobby         | skydiving     | card-games  | chess | singing       |

