.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-3::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: red, blood-red, light-blue, ivory
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, prince, blend, davidoff
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, board-games, hiking, baking
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, snowboarding, tennis, weightlifting
House: farmhouse, futuristic, craftsman, wooden
 1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the craftsman house##1
 3. the person who likes light-blue is the person who's hobby is baking##1
 4. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the wooden house##1
 5. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who likes ivory##1
 6. the wooden house is the person who likes light-blue##1
 7. the blend-smoker is on the left of the wooden house##1
 8. the farmhouse house is on the right of the craftsman house##1
 9. the davidoff-smoker is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
10. the prince-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
11. the wooden house is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
12. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3    |       4       |
| Color          | red    | ivory      | light-blue  | blood-red   |
| Cigar   | davidoff     | blend      | prince | pall-mall      |
| Hobby           | board-games       | writing         | baking  | hiking         |
| Sport         | basketball | snowboarding | tennis  | weightlifting |
| House     | craftsman       | farmhouse         | wooden   | futuristic        |

