.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-4::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, balloon-flower, orchid, dahlia
There are 4 different favourite colors: aquamarine, fuchsia, lavender, grey
House: wooden, craftsman, modern, townhouse
4 different pets are kept: cat, goat, guinea-pig, snake
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, rock-climbing, photography, drawing
 1. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 2. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
 4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far right##1
 5. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left##1
 6. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 7. the townhouse house is on the far right##1
 8. the person who likes grey is on the right of the modern house##1
 9. the craftsman house is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
10. the person who growsdaisy is on the far right##1
11. the person who growsorchid is on the far left##1
12. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Flower      | orchid   | dahlia   | balloon-flower      | daisy     |
| Color          | lavender     | aquamarine   | grey | fuchsia |
| House   | craftsman | modern | wooden   | townhouse       |
| Pet           | goat       | cat      | snake     | guinea-pig |
| Hobby     | fishing    | photography     | drawing     | rock-climbing     |

