.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-5::.
There 4 different types of food: kale, mango, potato, pumpkin
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, d&b, electronic, indie
House: modern, wooden, colonial, tower
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, juice, lemonade, iced-tea
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, cain, prince, dannemann
 1. the modern house is the dannemann-smoker##1
 2. the fan of electronic is on the far left##1
 3. the person drinking juice is on the far right##1
 4. the cain-smoker is the person eating potato##1
 5. the cain-smoker is on the right of the person eating mango##1
 6. the colonial house is on the far right##1
 7. the prince-smoker is on the right of the fan of house##1
 8. the dannemann-smoker is the modern house##1
 9. the person eating pumpkin is the prince-smoker##1
10. the fan of electronic is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
11. the person drinking milk is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
12. the wooden house is on the far left##1
13. the person drinking milk is on the right of the fan of indie##1
14. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Food          | kale       | mango     | potato     | pumpkin  |
| Music-Genre         | electronic  | indie | house | d&b  |
| House           | wooden | modern    | tower    | colonial |
| Beverage   | iced-tea    | lemonade   | milk | juice |
| Cigar           | pall-mall       | dannemann     | cain     | prince   |

