4 different pets are kept: rat, ferret, goat, dog
 1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the futuristic house##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person who's birthday is in november##1
 4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
 5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the craftsman house##1
 6. the craftsman house is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 7. the owner of the goat is the person who's birthday is in november##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the craftsman house##1
 9. the ranch-style house is on the far right##1
10. the person who's birthday is in april is the owner of the dog##1
11. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person drinking milk##1
12. the futuristic house is the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |      4      |
| Hobby         | dancing   | gardening | skydiving    | ferretd-games  |
| Beverage   | soy-milk    | milk | almond-milk      | iced-tea |
