City: boston, new-york, miami, venice
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, april, june, january
 1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the electrician##1
 3. the coach is on the far left##1
 4. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 5. the person drinking water is the person traveling to miami##1
 6. the person traveling to new-york is on the far right##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in january is the person drinking juice##1
 8. the librarian is on the left of the person eating peach##1
 9. the person drinking 7up is on the far right##1
10. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
11. the coach is the person drinking water##1
12. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| Beverage      | water     | juice      | soy-milk    | 7up           |
