.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-17::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: fuchsia, orange, red, blue
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, electronic, rock, blues
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, azalea, iris, lily
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, dog, hamster, mouse
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, thriller, family, superhero
 1. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
 2. the fan of techno is the person who growsamaryllis##1
 3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person who growslily##1
 4. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
 5. the person watching superhero movies is on the far right##1
 6. the fan of rock is on the far left##1
 7. the person who growslily is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
 8. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
 9. the person who likes fuchsia is the person watching thriller movies##1
10. the person who likes blue is the owner of the dog##1
11. the person watching family movies is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
12. the person who likes red is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |       2        |      3      |      4       |
| Color    | fuchsia     | orange  | blue       | red      |
| Music-Genre       | rock    | blues        | techno  | electronic      |
| Flower         | azalea  | lily | amaryllis | iris |
| Pet         | chinchilla | mouse          | dog         | hamster      |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller     | sports     | family       | superhero          |

