.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, mirinda, sprite, water
4 different games are played: scrabble, monopoly, whist, chess
City: venice, marseilles, liverpool, san-francisco
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: aconite, amaryllis, rose, marigold
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, dubstep, gospel, folk
 1. the person who growsrose is on the far left##1
 2. the person drinking mirinda is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 3. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the fan of country##1
 4. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
 5. the person playing whist is the person drinking sprite##1
 6. the person playing chess is the person drinking water##1
 7. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
 8. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the fan of folk##1
 9. the fan of dubstep is the person traveling to liverpool##1
10. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far left##1
11. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
12. the person playing chess is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |      3       |    4     |
| Beverage      | water       | sprite      | mirinda      | juice    |
| Game         | chess | whist | monopoly | scrabble  |
| City   | liverpool    | marseilles     | san-francisco      | venice |
| Flower   | rose  | marigold     | aconite    | amaryllis  |
| Music-Genre           | dubstep  | folk       | country          | gospel      |

