.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-19::.
There 4 different types of food: lime, plum, raspberry, tomato
There are 4 different favourite colors: lilac, apricot, mauve, ebony
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, chinese, russian, malaysian
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, september, july, december
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, juice, tea, cola
 1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far left##1
 2. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1
 3. the person drinking tea is the person who likes mauve##1
 4. the russian is on the right of the mexican##1
 5. the mexican is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 6. the malaysian is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
 7. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person eating lime##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person eating lime##1
 9. the chinese is on the right of the person eating plum##1
10. the person who's birthday is in december is the person eating raspberry##1
11. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
12. the person who likes apricot is on the far right##1
13. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |      3      |       4       |
| Food          | tomato      | plum     | lime        | raspberry     |
| Color         | mauve     | lilac    | ebony | apricot |
| Nationality   | mexican | russian  | chinese      | malaysian       |
| Birthday         | july      | june | september     | december        |
| Beverage     | tea   | cola     | fanta  | juice       |

