.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-20::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: sunflower, amaryllis, orchid, iris
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, parkour, weightlifting, biathlon
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, thai, russian, german
4 different pets are kept: cat, goat, goldfish, snake
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, vegafina, swisher, ritmeester
 1. the german is the person who's sport is rowing##1
 2. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
 3. the german is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 4. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the egyptian##1
 5. the owner of the goldfish is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 6. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 7. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the thai##1
 8. the egyptian is the tiparillo-smoker##1
 9. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
10. the person who growsiris is the owner of the snake##1
11. the owner of the snake is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
12. the owner of the snake is on the left of the russian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |       3        |      4      |
| Flower        | amaryllis    | iris        | sunflower        | orchid      |
| Sport       | weightlifting       | rowing       | parkour      | biathlon |
| Nationality         | thai | german | russian | egyptian      |
| Pet         | cat          | snake         | goat           | goldfish    |
| Cigar   | swisher         | vegafina       | ritmeester     | tiparillo   |

 